My body has been fighting the fight of its life, & I’m incredibly exhausted (physically & psychologically). Still, acute symptoms continue, and we (we meaning both us regular people and the medical community) just don’t know enough about this virus to be able to tell when things

For some of us, the fight doesn’t end once the fever ends (that was 2 wks ago for me) or once the terribly scary respiratory issues abate (that was a wk ago for me). The virus may remain in your body for longer, wreaking havoc,& like I do you may present post-viral complications.

So let me be your cautionary tale or that Tweet you screenshot and send to your incredulous uncle.
